item.description:
This fundraiser will aid all NH Liberty groups that are members as well as individuals that are members of the GSPL PAC.  This is Michele Bachmann's first visit to NH and we are fortunate to have her at this event. There will be "Political Chowder" to enjoy as well as other food and drink.  If you would like to volunteer to help at the event I am offering a few free passes.  I could use a handful more helpers if anyone is interested.  Contact me through GSPL_PAC@yahoo.com Here are the ticket prices:

General Admission $35.00

Couples General Admission $60.00

Student Admission $15.00

VIP Admission $100.00 this includes General Admission for 2 and a photo with Michele Bachmann.

These tickets are limited so do not wait.  If I can I will have some for sale at the door.
item.how_to_find_us: There will be sign in desks
item.why: Congresswoman Michele Bachmann (Minn) is speaking at The Granite State Patriots Liberty PAC's first fundraiser. The Rochester 912 Project is a member of the GSPL PAC and we can use your support. Jerry DeLemus is the GSPL PAC is the new PAC Chairman
item.name: Michele Bachmann in Barrington NH for Granite State Patriots Liberty PAC
